CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 12, 1963, pg. 8 reads: "Prize-Winners - Ten lucky persons at the Green Link Golf CLub's Pre-New Year's Masked Ball walked off with prizes for wearing the most unique masks. Left to right, seated: Elizabeth Alexander of Greenwich, Conn.; Alma Darks, Leo Willingham, Marion Saunders of Newburgh, N.Y., and Jean Mitchell.  Standing in rear: Biddie Higginbotham, Nellye [Nellie] Barron, Charles F. Williams, Muriel Saunders, Hardena Moore, Gladys Cralle and Rebecca Bledsol. - Harris Photo."
